FORMAT: 1A
HOST: https://polls.apiblueprint.org/

# MyPlantNote

使用者可以透過此程式設定植物資訊、澆水頻率。此專案為 MyPlantNote 後端，提供登入、awt 驗證、植物管理等一系列api。

## Get, Delete & Patch Plant [/api/plant/{id}]
`/api/plant`

### List Plants [GET]
根據 id 搜尋plant，若無指定 id 則列出所有plant。
+ Parameters
    + id (optional, string, `64ec14b96845963ad29c8e42`) ... plant id

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [
            {
                "name": "姬嚴龍",
                "type": "龍舌蘭",
                "owner": "64e5b84905bfe0cd6a203604",
                "startDate": "2023-08-28T03:30:01.938Z",
                "lastWateringDate": "2023-08-28T03:30:01.938Z",
                "wateringPeriod": "1d",
                "_id": "64ec14b96845963ad29c8e42",
                "createDate": "2023-08-28T03:30:01.938Z",
                "lastModifiedDate": "2023-08-28T03:30:01.938Z",
                "__v": 0
            }
        ]
### Delete Plant [DELETE]
根據 id 刪除plant。
+ Parameters
    + id (required, string, `64ec14b96845963ad29c8e42`) ... plant id

+ Request

    + Headers

            Authentication: Bearer JWT

+ Response 200 (application/json)

            {
                "message": "Delete a plant success"
            }
            

### Update Plant [PATCH]
根據 id 修改plant。
+ Parameters
    + id (required, string, `64ec14b96845963ad29c8e42`) ... plant id

+ Request

    + Headers

            Authentication: Bearer JWT

    + Body

            {
                "name": "姬嚴龍_modify",
                "type": "",
                "startDate": "",
                "lastWateringDate": "",
                "wateringPeriod": ""
            }

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "_id": "64ec14b96845963ad29c8e42",
            "name": "姬嚴龍_modify",
            "type": "64e8156a5b0c210d67908958",
            "owner": "64e5b84905bfe0cd6a203604",
            "startDate": "2023-08-28T03:30:01.938Z",
            "lastWateringDate": "2023-08-28T03:30:01.938Z",
            "wateringPeriod": "1d",
            "createDate": "2023-08-28T03:30:01.938Z",
            "lastModifiedDate": "2023-08-28T03:56:07.289Z",
            "__v": 0
        }

## Post a Plant [/api/plant/]
### Create a New Plant [POST]
新增 plant。
+ Request (application/json)
    + Headers

            Authentication: Bearer JWT

    + Body

            {
              "name": "姬嚴龍",
              "type": "龍舌蘭",
              "startDate": "",
              "lastWateringDate": "",
              "wateringPeriod": ""
            }

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Body

            {
                "name": "姬嚴龍",
                "type": "龍舌蘭",
                "owner": "64e5b84905bfe0cd6a203604",
                "startDate": "2023-08-28T03:30:01.938Z",
                "lastWateringDate": "2023-08-28T03:30:01.938Z",
                "wateringPeriod": "1d",
                "_id": "64ec14b96845963ad29c8e42",
                "createDate": "2023-08-28T03:30:01.938Z",
                "lastModifiedDate": "2023-08-28T03:30:01.938Z",
                "__v": 0
            }

## Get Personal Plant [/api/plant/personal/{type}]
`/api/plant/personal`

### List Personal Plant [GET]
取得屬於user的所有plant，若有攜帶type則指定搜尋的植物類型，否則為所有類型。
+ Parameters
    + type (optional ,string, `64e8156a5b0c210d67908958`) ... type id

+ Request

    + Headers

            Authentication: Bearer JWT

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "_id": "64ec14b96845963ad29c8e42",
            "name": "姬嚴龍_modify",
            "type": "64e8156a5b0c210d67908958",
            "owner": "64e5b84905bfe0cd6a203604",
            "startDate": "2023-08-28T03:30:01.938Z",
            "lastWateringDate": "2023-08-28T03:30:01.938Z",
            "wateringPeriod": "1d",
            "createDate": "2023-08-28T03:30:01.938Z",
            "lastModifiedDate": "2023-08-28T03:56:07.289Z",
            "__v": 0
        }
            
## Get User [/api/user/{id}]
