## Get, Update & Delete Note [/api/note/{id}]
`/api/note`

### List Note [GET]
根據 id 搜尋note，若無指定 id 則列出所有note。
+ Parameters
    + id (optional, string, `64ec14b96845963ad29c8e42`) ... noteId

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [
            {
                "name": "姬嚴龍",
                "type": "龍舌蘭",
                "owner": "64e5b84905bfe0cd6a203604",
                "startDate": "2023-08-28T03:30:01.938Z",
                "lastWateringDate": "2023-08-28T03:30:01.938Z",
                "wateringPeriod": "1d",
                "_id": "64ec14b96845963ad29c8e42",
                "createDate": "2023-08-28T03:30:01.938Z",
                "lastModifiedDate": "2023-08-28T03:30:01.938Z",
                "__v": 0
            }
        ]

### Update Note [PATCH]
根據 id 更新 Note
+ Parameters
    + id (required, string, `64fa9624e6558e3baa294770`) ...noteId

+ Request

    + Headers

            Authentication: Bearer JWT
    
    + Body
    
            {
                "title": "note title update",
                "pictures": [],
                "content": "for update testing"
            }

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "note": {
                "plantId": "64eeed5986534943180d9b90",
                "author": "64e5b84905bfe0cd6a203604",
                "title": "note title update",
                "pictures": [],
                "content": "for update testing",
                "_id": "64fa9624e6558e3baa294770",
                "createDate": "2023-09-08T03:33:56.023Z",
                "lastModifiedDate": "2023-09-08T03:33:56.023Z",
                "__v": 0
            },
            "plant": "64eeed5986534943180d9b90"
        }
        
### Delete Note [DELETE]
根據 id 刪除 Note
+ Parameters
    + id (required, string, `64fa9624e6558e3baa294770`) ...noteId

+ Request

    + Headers

            Authentication: Bearer JWT

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "message": "Delete note sucess"
        }
        

## Post Note [/api/note/{plantId}]
`/api/note/{plantId}`

### Create Note [POST]
在指定的植物下建立新的筆記
+ Parameters
    + plantId (required, string, `64eeed5986534943180d9b90`) ...plantId

+ Request

    + Headers

            Authentication: Bearer JWT
    
    + Body
    
            {
                "title": "note title",
                "pictures": [],
                "content": "for testing"
            }

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "note": {
                "plantId": "64eeed5986534943180d9b90",
                "author": "64e5b84905bfe0cd6a203604",
                "title": "note title",
                "pictures": [],
                "content": "for testing",
                "_id": "64fa9624e6558e3baa294770",
                "createDate": "2023-09-08T03:33:56.023Z",
                "lastModifiedDate": "2023-09-08T03:33:56.023Z",
                "__v": 0
            },
            "plant": "64eeed5986534943180d9b90"
        }
        
## Get, Update & Delete Article [/api/article/{id}]
`/api/article/{id}`

### List Article [GET]
根據 id 搜尋 article，若無指定 id 則列出所有 article。

+ Parameters
    + id (optional, string, `64eff95e2ed9f8c50ce5c567`) ... article id

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [
          {
            "_id": "64eff95e2ed9f8c50ce5c567",
            "title": "test1",
            "author": "64e5b84905bfe0cd6a203604",
            "pictures": [ ],
            "plantType": "64e8156a5b0c210d67908958",
            "content": "something",
            "createDate": "2023-08-31T02:22:22.909Z",
            "lastModifiedDate": "2023-08-31T02:22:22.910Z",
            "__v": 1
          }
        ]

### Update Article [PATCH]
根據 id 更新 article

+ Parameters
    + id (required, string, `64eff95e2ed9f8c50ce5c567`) ... article id
    
+ Request
    
    + Headers

            Authentication: Bearer JWT
    
    + Body
    
            {
              "title": "for update testing",
            }
    
+ Response 200 (application/json)

          {
            "_id": "64eff95e2ed9f8c50ce5c567",
            "title": "for update testing",
            "author": "64e5b84905bfe0cd6a203604",
            "pictures": [ ],
            "plantType": "64e8156a5b0c210d67908958",
            "content": "something",
            "createDate": "2023-08-31T02:22:22.909Z",
            "lastModifiedDate": "2023-08-31T02:22:22.910Z",
            "__v": 1
          }
          
### Delete Article [DELETE]
根據 id 刪除 article

+ Parameters
    + id (required, string, `64eff95e2ed9f8c50ce5c567`) ... article id
    
+ Request
    
    + Headers

            Authentication: Bearer JWT
    
+ Response 200 (application/json)

            {
                "message": "Delete article success"
            }
            
